#41500
Before the Sacred Well - Grove of Worship~
Tall oaks stand sturdily around a great clearing.  Their gnarled limbs
reach down gently, welcoming visitors to this holy place as the soft wind
causes their thick, twisted branches to whisper greetings to all
worshippers here.  Pale light breaks down faintly through the thick, dark
overhead canopy of leaves, speckling the grassy area all around the
sacred well with glowing patches of warm beauty.  It is quite shady
beneath the oaks; cool air brushes against you and carries upon it the
muted calls of songbirds from all across the island.
